  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-grid">
        <div class="intro-content">
          <h2>Professional Concrete Services in {city}</h2>
          <p>{city} is known worldwide for its crystal-clear springs and mermaids, but locals know it as a beautiful place to call home. The Weeki Wachee area encompasses diverse properties—from waterfront homes along the Weeki Wachee River to quiet inland neighborhoods surrounded by Florida's natural beauty.</p>
          
          <p>At Brooksville Concrete Co., we understand that Weeki Wachee's unique environment requires specialized concrete solutions. The proximity to water, sandy soils, and Florida's intense weather patterns all influence how concrete should be installed. Our team brings over 15 years of local experience to every project.</p>
          
          <p>Whether you're looking to replace an aging driveway, create a stunning patio for entertaining, or install a foundation for a workshop or pole barn, we have the expertise to deliver outstanding results. Our knowledge of Weeki Wachee's specific conditions ensures your concrete will look great and last for decades.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-content">
          <h3>Our {city} Services</h3>
          <ul class="why-list">
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Concrete Driveways</strong>
                Durable driveways engineered for Weeki Wachee's soil conditions. Standard and decorative options available.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Patios & Outdoor Living</strong>
                Create the perfect space to enjoy Weeki Wachee's beautiful weather with a custom concrete patio.
              </div>
