                <strong>Stamped Concrete</strong>
                Beautiful decorative finishes that complement your home's natural surroundings.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Slabs & Foundations</strong>
                Solid foundations for sheds, workshops, and outbuildings on your Weeki Wachee property.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
